---
import DocsLayout from "../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro";
---

<DocsLayout title="Documentation" description="Complete documentation for MJO-LITUI component library" currentPath="/docs">
    <article class="prose">
        <h1>Welcome to MJO-LITUI Documentation</h1>
        <p class="lead">
            MJO-LITUI is a modern Lit component library designed to help developers build beautiful, accessible, and performant user interfaces with ease.
        </p>
        <h2>What is MJO-LITUI?</h2>
        <p>
            MJO-LITUI is a comprehensive component library built on top of Lit, providing a collection of reusable, customizable components that follow modern
            web standards and accessibility guidelines.
        </p>
        <div class="feature-highlight">
            <h3>Key Features</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>TypeScript First:</strong> Built with TypeScript for excellent developer experience</li>
                <li><strong>Accessibility:</strong> WCAG 2.1 compliant with keyboard navigation support</li>
                <li><strong>Customizable:</strong> Extensive theming system with CSS custom properties</li>
                <li><strong>Performance:</strong> Optimized for speed with minimal bundle size</li>
                <li><strong>Framework Agnostic:</strong> Works with any framework or vanilla JavaScript</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <h2>Getting Started</h2>
        <p>Ready to start building? Check out our quick start guide to get up and running in just a few minutes.</p>
        <div class="action-cards">
            <a href="/docs/installation" class="action-card">
                <div class="action-card-icon">
                    <svg class="action-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4-4m0 0l-4 4m4-4v12"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Installation</h3>
                <p>Learn how to install and set up MJO-LITUI in your project.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/docs/quick-start" class="action-card">
                <div class="action-card-icon">
                    <svg class="action-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Quick Start</h3>
                <p>Get started quickly with our step-by-step guide.</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/docs/components" class="action-card">
                <div class="action-card-icon">
                    <svg class="action-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Components</h3>
                <p>Explore our collection of ready-to-use components.</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/docs/themes" class="action-card">
                <div class="action-card-icon">
                    <svg class="action-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
