        <h2>Community & Support</h2>

        <p>Need help or want to contribute? Our community is here to help you succeed.</p>

        <div class="community-links">
            <a href="https://github.com/username/mjo-litui" class="community-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
